<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Conferma Evento</title>

    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }
        table {
            border-spacing: 0;
        }
        img {
            border: 0;
            display: block;
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
        }
        .email-container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 650px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            color: #333333;
        }
        .header {
            background: #1e3a8a;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3a8a, #3b82f6);
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .section {
            padding: 30px 20px;
        }
        .divider {
            height: 1px;
            background-color: #e5e7eb;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background-color: #3b82f6;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #e2e8f0;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #333333;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .social-icons a {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            margin: 0 8px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 50%;
            line-height: 40px;
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

    </style>

</head>
<body>
<center>
    <table role="presentation" class="email-container">

        <tr>
            <td class="header">
                <center>
                <img src="cid:logo" alt="logo" width="50" height="50" ></center>
                <h1 style="margin: 0; font-size: 24px;">$nome, ci sei anche tu!</h1>
            </td>
        </tr>

        <tr>
            <td class="section">
                <p>Grazie per il tuo ordine e per aver scelto il nostro servizio!</p>
                <p><strong>Organizzazione Eventi Enterprise</strong></p>

                <div class="divider"></div>

                <p>Ti confermiamo i seguenti dettagli relativi al tuo ordine:</p>

                <h2 style="font-size: 20px; background-color: #fbbf24; padding: 6px 12px; border-radius: 4px; display: inline-block;">$evento</h2>

                <table role="presentation" width="100%" style="background-color: #f0f7ff; border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6; margin: 20px 0;">
                    <tr>
                        <td style="padding: 10px;">
                            <img src="cid:pin" alt="pin" width="16" height="16" style="vertical-align: middle;">
                            <h3>
                            <strong>$luogo</strong><br></h3>
                            <p>
                                $indirizzo
                            </p>
                            <img src="cid:calendar" alt="calendar" width="16" height="16" style="vertical-align: middle;">
                            <strong>$data</strong>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </table>

                <div class="divider"></div>

                <h3>Dettagli Biglietto</h3>
                <p><strong>1x$posto</strong><br>
                    <strong>Nominativo: </strong> $nome $cognome<br>
                    <strong>In Zona:</strong> $zona<br>
                    <strong>Con:</strong> $features
                </p>
                <center>
                <a href="https://www.google.com/calendar/render?action=TEMPLATE&text=$evento&dates=$formattedStart/$formattedEnd&details=Ingresso+$posto+per+$nome+$cognome+luogo=$luogo+$indirizzo" class="button" target="_blank">
                    + Aggiungi al Google Calendar +</a>

                <a href="$baseUrl/api/evento/$eventoId/ics" download="evento.ics">
                    <button style="padding: 10px; background-color: #4CAF50; color: white; border: none; border-radius: 5px;">
                        Esporta Evento (.ics)
                    </button>
                </a>
                </center>

            </td>
        </tr>

        <tr>
            <td class="footer">
                <!-- Sezione Social (senza link) -->
                <table role="presentation" align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
                    <tr>
                        <td style="padding: 0 5px;">
                            <img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/2111/2111463.png" alt="Instagram" width="32" height="32" style="display: block;">
                        </td>
                        <td style="padding: 0 5px;">
                            <img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/733/733547.png" alt="Facebook" width="32" height="32" style="display: block;">
                        </td>
                        <td style="padding: 0 5px;">
                            <img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/1384/1384060.png" alt="YouTube" width="32" height="32" style="display: block;">
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </table>


                <p style="margin-top: 20px;"><strong>Eventra | Customer Care</strong></p>
                <p>Per favore non rispondere a questa email. Se hai dubbi o domande, visita le nostre <a href="#" style="color: #1e3a8a; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold;">FAQ</a>.</p>
                <p>&copy; 2025 Eventra. Tutti i diritti riservati.</p>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</center>
</body>
</html>
